      </p>
     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA08d173n1-ptr" id="PJA08d173n1">1</a>
      <p>See Lovell to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, 14 Oct., 2d letter, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-08-02-0140&amp;expandNote=PJA08d146n1#PJA08d146n1" class="document">note 1</a> (above).</p>
     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA08d173n2-ptr" id="PJA08d173n2">2</a>
      <p>Thus in <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ manuscript ]">MS</abbr>.</p>
     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA08d173n3-ptr" id="PJA08d173n3">3</a>
      <p>See Lovell to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-08-02-0151" class="document">19 Oct.</a> (above).</p>
     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA08d173n4-ptr" id="PJA08d173n4">4</a>
      <p>The following two sentences appear after a short space in the line, and in a somewhat larger, less careful hand, suggesting that <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> added them as an afterthought. They refer to a report in Lovells letter of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-08-02-0151" class="document">19 Oct.</a> (above).</p>
     </div>
